<p class="ql-align-center">陕西省029-63917811/63917837</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">西安市029-81709651</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">宝鸡市0917-3419686</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">咸阳市029-33351068</p>
